@node "History" "History"

History
=======

       - Version 1.01 (11.04.95) : first distributed version.

       - Version 1.02 (15.06.95) : some  bugs  fixed, some  changes  in the
  @{"preferences editor" LINK PreferencesEditor}, documentation completed.

       - Version 1.03 (28.06.95) : the @{"Set date" LINK SetDate} function  has been  impro-
  ved.  Added  "%ps" and "%sr"  for  the @{"External tool" LINK ExternalTool} function.  Fixed  a
  little bug in the @{"preferences editor" LINK PreferencesEditor}. Text viewer improved.

       - Version 1.04 (19.07.95) : fixed a  bug in  the text viewer. @{"Quit" LINK Quit},
  @{"Reread preferences" LINK ReadPrefs} and @{"Iconify" LINK Iconify} functions have been improved.  Arguments
  and tooltypes support.  Added the "Use Workbench colours" function in the
  @{"preferences editor" LINK PreferencesEditor} (@{"Screen" LINK Screen}). Fixed some other little bugs. Now Ordering
  recognizes catalogs with internal mode (see @{"Filetypes" LINK FileTypes}).

       - Version 1.05 (14.09.95) : fixed a bug  in the moving  of the mouse
  pointer when opening a window.  Better keys handling.  Fixed a bug in the
  short-cut key  editing (@{"buttons" LINK Buttons}).  Screens  openings  improved.  English
  documentation corrected. Buttons may be located between windows.  Fixed a
  bug in the @{"Reread preferences" LINK ReadPrefs} function.

       - Version 1.06 (09.03.96) : @{"Rename" LINK Rename} function improved. Short-cut key
  edition improved (buttons).  Fixed some bugs.  Better keys handling.  Now
  you can select paths position.  Added the "Immediate scrolling" option to
  the @{"Read" LINK Read} function.

       - Version 1.07 (29.08.96) : windows and entries selections improved.
  Added the  possibility  to  quit  the @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic} by  clicking  the left
  mousebutton.  Added a horizontal scrolling  in the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}.  Danish,
  Italian and Norwegian translations.  Installer script  improved.  Fixed a
  bug in the @{"Delete" LINK Delete} function. Fixed a bug when reading a directory.  Docu-
  mentation a bit improved.  Fixed a bug in the @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic}.  Cycle gadget
  in the @{"Relabel" LINK Relabel} function widened. @{"Get version" LINK GetVersion} function improved. Fixed a
  bug in the search string function. MagicWB style icons.

       - Version 1.08 (20.10.96) : fixed  a  bug in the  hard disks  format
  process.  Fixed a bug in  the paths scrolling.  Fixed a couple of bugs in
  the @{"Clone" LINK Clone} function.  Fixed a bug in the @{"Rename" LINK Rename} function (rename icon as
  well).  Fixed a  couple of  bugs in the @{"text viewer" LINK Read} (Immediate scrolling
  and last line display).  The @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic} may now show the first frame of
  an animation.  Added the  possibility to abort an images showing sequence
  by pressing ESC. Screens openings improved.  Swedish translation. Italian
  translation corrected.

       - Version 1.09 (18.12.96) : fixed  a  bug  in  the @{"Hexadecimal read" LINK HexRead}
  function.  Scrolling  in  the @{"Select buffer" LINK SelectBuffer} and @{"Clear buffers" LINK ClearBuffers} functions
  debugged and improved.

       - Version 1.10 (26.01.97) : fixed  a  bug  in  the  @{"Clone" LINK Clone} function.
  English documentation corrected.

       - Version 1.11 (13.01.98) : fixed a bug in the backward search func-
  tion of the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}.  Improvement  and fixed some bugs in the search
  functions of the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}. Added the "Find all occurrences" option in
  the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}.  Now @{"text viewer" LINK Read} supports  IFF-FTXT files.  Display of
  free memory improved.  Better  CyberGraphics support in the @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic}.
  Fixed a  bug in the @{"DiskCopy" LINK DiskCopy} function.  Fixed a  bug in the @{"Copy" LINK Copy}, @{"Move" LINK Move}
  and @{"Clone" LINK Clone} functions.  Fixed a bug in the keys handling. @{"Action" LINK Action} function
  improved.  Search functions of the @{"text viewer" LINK Read} fixed and improved. Added
  "%fse" and "%rfse",  and fixed three bugs in the @{"External tool" LINK ExternalTool} function.
  Fixed a bug in the @{"Relabel a volume" LINK Relabel} function.

       - Version 1.12 (09.05.98) : Fixed a bug in the @{"Copy" LINK Copy} function. Fixed
  a bug in the filetype recognition.  Fixed a bug in the @{"Delete" LINK Delete} function.
  @{"Memorize selection" LINK MemorizeSelection} and @{"Restore selection" LINK RestoreSelection} functions entirely rewritten.
  Added the opportunity to print a file in hexadecimal in the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}.
  Fixed  a bug in the @{"Hunt files" LINK Hunt} function.  Better  mouse handling in the
  scrolling. Polish translation. @{"Show font" LINK ShowFont} function a bit improved.

       - Version 1.13 (24.06.98) : Fixed  a  bug  in  the  @{"Move" LINK Move}  function.
  Default configuration improved.

       - Version 1.14 (27.07.98) : German translation.  Polish  translation
  corrected. Fixed a bug with the long filenames.

       - Version 1.15 (25.10.98) : Fixed a  bug when  reading a  directory.
  Added some short-cut keys in the @{"text viewer" LINK Read}. English documentation cor-
  rected. Added an "All" button in the @{"Set date" LINK SetDate} function. NewIcons support
  in the @{"Show icon" LINK ShowIcon} function. Fixed a bug in the @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic}. Italian do-
  cumentation corrected. Better keys handling.

       - Version 1.16 (02.02.99) : Swedish  translation  corrected.  German
  translation  corrected.  Screens openings  improved in  the @{"ILBM viewer" LINK ShowPic}.
  Screens openings  improved.  Loading  of @{"external tools" LINK ExternalTool} improved  in the
  @{"preferences editor" LINK PreferencesEditor}. Fixed a bug in the @{"Get version" LINK GetVersion} function. Fixed a bug
  in  the @{"External tool" LINK ExternalTool} function (with %dr).  Screens openings improved in
  the @{"preferences editor" LINK PreferencesEditor}. Fixed a bug in the @{"Show icon" LINK ShowIcon} function.

       - Version 1.17 (22.04.99) : Fixed a little bug when reading directo-
  ries.  Works better with  large hard drives (more than 4 GB).  Added  the
  @{"Select a directory" LINK SelectDir} function.  Better error handling when a typed path is
  wrong.

       - Version 1.17 (17.02.01) : Some bugs fixed.
